      "content": "The second principle of Open-Source Capitalism is incentive alignment via tokens and revenue sharing. Powerhouse uses Proof of Work Tokens (POWTs) to compensate contributors fairly over time, enabling deferred compensation models that align long-term incentives. POWTs represent a stake in the success of the network, linking compensation to measurable contributions and making contributors invested in the outcomes of the projects they support.",
